videos.description: Collin Sexton gets a steal and finds Donta Hall who throws down the transition jam. On the next possession, Sexton delivers a nice dish to Hall for the one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Albama's Sexton-Hall connection lethal on offense

videos.description: Braxton Key comes across court and blocks Wesley Meyers shot off the backboard.
videos.headline: Alabama's Key gets a monster block

videos.description: Braxton Key snatches the rebound then instinctively throws it up to Donta Hall for the alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Alabama's Hall throws down nasty slam

videos.description: Collin Sexton makes a nice pass to Herb Jones who throws down the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Sexton's dime leads to Alabama dunk
